            "channel_id": "ch_revenue_ops",
            "text": "Lifecycle stage automation update - effective immediately:\n\n1. Contacts whose Notes column contains 'Do Not Move' must be skipped regardless of their day count or usage trend. These accounts are in a restricted cohort pending engagement verification.\n2. Contacts whose Notes column contains 'Manual Review Required' must also be skipped -- do not update their stage until cleared.\n3. These rules are in addition to the existing 'do not modify' and 'under review' notes exclusions from the Q1 ops-director email.\n4. Continue using the Q1 ops-director lifecycle classification rules (At-Risk=Declining, Onboarding <30 days, Growing 30-90, Mature >90).\n5. Batch reference for this run: LCSTG-267-Q1 (unchanged).\n\nDo not process any contacts in restricted cohorts."
          }
